Was slightly off the heezy a few shots and some glasses in when I thought to myself, "Damn it's a vibe in here" LMAO. But really it is tho. The ajummas are direct and to the point just like the food itself. It's no frills here. Tender delicious yummy galbi plus soup plus this lil fried fish plus some drank for like $30 sumn dollars? I'm down.
